<div class="col-12">
  <h1>Messer Bracket Setup</h1>
  <p>
    Wire up each draw slot so that approving a result automatically advances the
    winning team into its next-round slot. This is a once-a-season job — set it up
    when the new draw is created.
  </p>
  <p>
    For each slot you set which slot the winner feeds into (<strong>next slot</strong>)
    and which side of that match they take (<strong>H</strong>ome or <strong>A</strong>way).
    Leave both blank for a section final.
  </p>

  <a class="btn btn-primary mb-2 me-2" href="/admin/messer-bracket/a-section">Wire up A Section</a>
  <a class="btn btn-primary mb-2" href="/admin/messer-bracket/b-section">Wire up B Section</a>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="/messer-results">← Back to Messer Results</a></p>
</div>

